<event name="STATION_SICK_MARKET" unique="true">
	<text>An inconspicuous station is posted here, probably an honest trader looking to make a profit somewhere with larger crowds.</text>
	<ship load="SHIP_STATIONS_GENERIC" hostile="false"/>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Contact them to see if they want to trade.</text>
		<event>
			<text>The station's leader appears on your vid-screen, coughing. "W-what? Oh, sorry. No trading for now, we're all sick. This damn place draws in thousands of ships from all over the galaxy, god knows what kinds of diseases it brings. We're probably dying of some exotic Mantis flu or something, if that even exists."</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Offer what supplies you can muster. [-10~, -2|]</text>
				<event>
					<text>"This won't help much, but it's much appreciated. Glad to know there's some kind souls out there still. I can't offer much in return, but we can use our automated repair drones to fix up some hull for you."</text>
