				<event>
					<text>The station's crew is frightened at first that they're under attack, but soon realize your healing bursts are only improving their condition. "How peculiar, I've never seen medical supplies such as those. Would you be willing to sell them to us, in case this sort of situation ever occurs again?"</text>
