<textList name="TUCO_DRINK">
    <text>The Rockman slides you a shot of some suspicious looking alien goop. It's surprisingly tasty. Two drunken pirates get into a brawl behind you and are escorted out.</text>
    <text>The bartender polishes a glass and hands you another shot. This time it's a relatively normal looking glass of liquid, but it makes your insides burn like fire. You cough and spit it out. You catch some Rebels behind you laughing.</text>
    <text>You're handed a glass of a putrid smelling substance, which you're told is freshly bottled Slug slime. When the bartender isn't looking, you pour it down the sink.</text>
    <text>The Rock gives you a glass of clear liquid. It doesn't taste like anything. The chattering in the background quiets down for a second when a drunken Slug falls off the stage, then goes back to its usual volume.</text>
    <text>The drink tastes an awful lot like urine, and your suspicions are confirmed when the Rockman informs you it's Human waste, considered a delicacy in some areas.</text>
    <text>While you down the latest shot, you watch a Mantis juggle flaming skulls. The crowd breaks into applause until the Mantis catches on fire and runs screaming out of the inn.</text>
    <text>As you drink the green substance in your bottle you observe the crowd further. It's an interesting bunch. You can see enemies staring at each other across the room, and glancing away when their gaze meets.</text>
    <text>You choke down the horrid substance given to you by the bartender, a strange chunky white substance. The Rockman tells you it's expired milk from a space whale.</text>
</textList>

