<event name="TUCO_SEARCH">   
	<text>Before you can even begin searching, a shout echoes throughout the casino. People turn to stare as a Rockman in pirate paint with a filthy moss beard and eyepatch with an elegant tuxedo is dragged out by two burly Rockmen bouncers. On his way out, the pirate exclaims "You can't do this to me! Do you know who I am? I am the dread pirate Tuco, the most feared man in the entire galaxy!" The Rockmen ignore him and continue to carry him outside.</text>
	<choice hidden="true">
		<text>Follow.</text>
		<event>
			<text>You aren't sure what you plan to do, but the situation has you curious. You follow them outside to see Tuco heading back to a large cruiser with yellow pirate paint. Not long after, the ship powers up, its weapons come online, and he's firing at the casino! A few enforcer ships fly out to meet him, but it's uncertain who will win the fight.</text>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Aid Tuco.</text>
				<event>
					<text>You power up your weapons and attack one of the enforcers head on. It looks suspiciously like a Rebel transport that was painted over again, but that doesn't matter.</text>
					<ship load="SHIP_CASINO" hostile="true"/>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Continue...</text>
						<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
					</choice>
				</event>
			</choice>
			<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Aid the Casino Enforcers.</text>
				<event>
					<text>You're sure the casino will have a reward for you if you save them from Tuco's attack.</text>
					<ship load="SHIP_TUCO" hostile="true"/>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Continue...</text>
						<event load="COMBAT_CHECK"/>
					</choice>
				</event>
