	<text>You've arrived at the location of the Federation distress call... except there's no Federation ship here. Instead, there's a massive Hacker cruiser waiting for you! "You think you're clever? Do you even know how long it took to sssset up all thossse ssstationss? Well, it doesssn't matter now. Thisss isss what you get for crossssing the Hacker clan'ssss path!"</text>
